data.description: Well upgraded South Vandenberg Village home with space for everyone.  Enter through a Grand Custom front door from the inviting front porch patio. This 2 story home features an open kitchen, dining room and formal living room space accented with lots of natural light through newer paned windows and newer plank flooring. Have coffee on your walk out deck overlooking your private rear yard.  3 Bedrooms & full bath upstairs.  Enjoy the downstairs Great room with brick fireplace and full bathroom and access the large rear yard and 2 covered patios from downstairs. 4 minisplit heater/air conditioner units covering all 5 rooms throughout up & downstairs with individual thermostats. Don't forget to check out the workshop/shed with power and the pull down storage in the covered patio. 40 feet of gated RV parking in rear and extended driveway in front.  Located just minutes from Vandenberg Space Force Base main entrance and easy access to PCH Hwy 1 for Santa Barbara commuters. This home is worth your attention today!
